if you do not want to show long form, instead you want to show short form - progressive profiling
nobody like to fill the long form
if you want to get the all important data at the same time not compromising with the user experience - we use progressive profiling


steps:
1. In form settings - click settings - enable the progressive profiling
2.  GO to field details - you can see progressive profiling box
3.  drag fields into progressive profiling box
4. click on box and control blank fields. if its 1 blank fields it shows along the existing
